Third-party components

NovaVPN links against and redistributes third-party software under their own
licences. Full licence texts are installed alongside the application and are
listed in ThirdParty/README.md.

  nlohmann/json   MIT
  Catch2          Boost Software License 1.0 (tests only, not redistributed)
  Wintun          Prosperity Public Licence / commercial - see WireGuard LLC
  OpenSSL         Apache License 2.0
  OpenVPN         GNU General Public License v2
  SQLite          public domain

The GPLv2 terms of the OpenVPN engine apply to the engine component and to any
derivative of it. NovaVPN's own source, as covered by the MIT licence above, is
kept separable from the engine through the plugin ABI described in
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md so that each component's licence can be honoured
independently.
